{"word":"ζαχρηής","slug":"ζαχρηής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n46119\" key=\"zaxrhh/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ζαχρηής</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ές</itype>, used only in pl., <sense id=\"n46119.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">attacking violently, furious, raging</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μένος Βορέαο καὶ ἄλλων ζαχρηῶν ἀνέμων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:525\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.525</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-χρει-</foreign> most codd.); of warriors, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ζαχρηεῖς . . κατὰ κρατ ερὰς ὑσμίνας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:12:347\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.347</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:684\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.684</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζαχραής, ζαχρειής</foreign>. (From <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ζᾰ-</foreign> and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">χράω</foreign> (B); cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπιχράω</foreign> (B).)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}